<ITEM>Mi&s;s Wilkin&s;on.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Neptune,</LABEL>
<ITEM>Ma&s;ter Se&s;tini.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Bacchus,</LABEL>
<ITEM>Ma&s;ter Langri&s;t.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Plutus,</LABEL>
<ITEM>Ma&s;ter Se&s;tini.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Mercury,</LABEL>
<ITEM>Mi&s;s Decamp.</ITEM>
<LABEL>Do<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter">us,</LABEL>
